item.title: Does .: Project Acheron :. have a trojan?
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

http://virusscan.jotti.org/en

Its the most reliable online scanner, and even if one scanner thinks it is a virus I would not recommend to open it.
If it claims it is safe and there are no bait “openme.exe” files lying around I would still check the main method in the super class to make sure the server is not trying to open and create anything malicious like registry edits.
